{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">UNLEASH THE MUTANT WITHIN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into the vibrant, bio-cyberpunk world of Diamond Core Metropolis, where chaos reigns in every arena. Take control of a powerful mutant, master unique abilities, and fight for survival in an electrifying dystopian future. <br><br>Play the first 4 chapters of the <strong>Singleplayer Story Mode</strong> or dominate the thrilling <strong>5v5 Online Multiplayer</strong> modes during the Open-Beta weekends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481390/extras/gif_hovergrease2_mutantgirls_kimmyfrog_peanut_bunny_616px_8mb.gif?t=1739119690\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THE BIO-CYBERPUNK WORLD OF HOVERGREASE 2</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The world of HoverGrease is a bio-cyberpunk dystopian future Earth, where mankind has unlocked many of the secrets of the human genome.\u00a0 It\u2019s a place over-saturated with AI, cybernetic enhancements, and biotechnology. Mutations are rare, but not uncommon.<br><br>Fight in the Downtown streets of Pine Bay, blast your enemies off the platforms of the Skyrise District, and survive the waves of attacks from the shores of Razer beach.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481390/extras/gif_hovergrease2_madeyebull_scarletfox_616px_8mb.gif?t=1739119690\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FIND THE MUTANT FOR YOUR PLAY STYLE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pick from <strong>10 mutants</strong> with over <strong>180 weapons and attacks</strong>, and blast your way to success.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481390/extras/steam_aboutGraphics_heroSelection.png?t=1739119690\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481390/extras/5mutants.jpg?t=1739119690\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play with Kimmy Frog for rockets, Madeye Bull or Piggy for melee dash-and-slash, snipe your enemy with Scarlet and Billy Bo, or support the team with Labrat Perry and Peanut Piper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481390/extras/gif_hovergrease2_gameplaytrailer_616px_10mb.gif?t=1739119690\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EASY TO PICK UP, HARD TO MASTER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">HoverGrease 2 is incredibly easy to pick up.<br><br>Despite its top-down perspective widely associated with MOBAs, HoverGrease 2 plays more like a shooter (WASD+mouse or twin-stick gamepad). Skills are more important than \u2018builds\u2019, but strategy and teamwork trump both.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481390/extras/steam__mainCapsule_kimmy.jpg?t=1739119690\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SINGLE PLAYER STORY &amp; MULTIPLAYER GAME MODES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in the world of HoverGrease 2 and play the <i>story mode</i>. Then join your friends online in a <i>team-based multiplayer online</i> game that will challenge your skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Avaiable in the DEMO:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 4 chapters of the Singleplayer story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3 maps for multiplayer game (limited server access)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All 10 unique mutants are playable</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play your way! Mouse &amp; Keyboard, Gamepad, or  Steam Deck</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481390/extras/steam_steamdeck.png?t=1739119690\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2